person.bio: Dina 1 year experience in CloudComputing, getting her Bachelor degree in Communication Engineer. Free time = Reading, Cooking, watching movies and keep in touch with technology. Engineer fell in love with Threefold I believe in ThreeFold goals and ideas. Plus, it has lots of bright minds I'm so proud to work/learn from them on a daily basis.
